WEBVTT

00:10.051 --> 00:16.009
And finally, perhaps a message to students of the London School for Business and Finance.

00:16.097 --> 00:18.778
What would your message be for the future, for them?

00:19.284 --> 00:21.963
Make the most of  the contacts you're gonna make here...

00:22.111 --> 00:27.787
...because you'll form relationships and friendships and contacts that will be immensely important in later life.

00:28.222 --> 00:32.145
And you know, I really do believe it's the world today that works by connectivity.

00:32.614 --> 00:34.973
And those people that are well-connected,...

00:35.341 --> 00:40.591
...and that's not just a matter of technology, it's also about forming the right partnerships and relationships,...

00:40.679 --> 00:42.208
...those that are well-connected will do well.

